net.starype.minigameapi.features.polyvalent

Class RespawnManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.starype.minigameapi.features.polyvalent.RespawnManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Feature, Linkable, org.bukkit.event.Listener

    public class RespawnManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements Feature, org.bukkit.event.Listener, Linkable

    RespawnManager is a Polyvalent Feature, therefore it that can be used as a feature alone or as a sub feature depending of the GameDivision instance, to manage respawns of players.

    It also implements Listener interface, because we use a PlayerRespawnEvent and a EntityDamageEvent

    Author:
    Askigh
